<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><!--
    strings.xml - String Resources
    All text strings used in the app should be defined here.
    Benefits:
    1. Easy to translate the app (just create strings-fr.xml, strings-hi.xml, etc.)
    2. Easy to change text without modifying multiple Java/XML files
    3. Android Studio flags hardcoded strings as warnings
-->
